00:00:13.074 --> 00:00:20.080
Hi! Welcome to Aha Emi Ruchi!

00:00:31.903 --> 00:00:37.528
What are you cooking?
Green Gram &amp; Ridge Gourd Fry

00:00:41.278 --> 00:00:44.277
Ingredients required to make Green Gram &amp; Ridge Gourd Fry

00:00:44.686 --> 00:00:55.940
Grated Ridge Gourd, Green Gram, Dry Red Chilli, Garlic, 
Cumin, Curry Leaves, Seasoning Seeds, Chilli Powder, Salt, Oil

00:01:07.065 --> 00:01:14.473
Take a pan and heat some oil

00:01:20.140 --> 00:01:40.275
Add some dry red chilli, seasoning seeds - mustard seeds, white lentil, bengal gram, cumin, garlic

00:01:51.995 --> 00:01:59.409
Add a few curry leaves

00:02:18.357 --> 00:02:22.358
Peel the ridge gourd and grind it, then squeeze out the moisture to get a dry powder texture

00:02:23.991 --> 00:02:30.417
Add a cup of the ground ridge gourd

00:03:09.374 --> 00:03:16.662
Add 1/2 a cup of boiled green gram

00:03:17.727 --> 00:03:24.304
Add some salt for taste

00:03:27.478 --> 00:03:30.918
Add some red chilli powder

00:03:44.525 --> 00:04:00.541
Take it in a serving bowl and garnish with some cashews

